        "text": "=Analyze this e-commerce product image for catalog search.\n\nMOST IMPORTANT: Identify the EXACT product category first (shoes, t-shirt, dress, pants, bag, watch, etc). This must be the FIRST keyword. Never confuse product categories.\n\nThen describe:\n- Specific subcategory (sneaker, sandal, boot, polo, hoodie, etc)\n- Primary and secondary colors\n- Visible materials (leather, cotton, mesh, synthetic, denim, etc)\n- Distinct features (laces, stripes, logo, pattern, zipper, etc)\n- Target demographic (Men's, Women's, Kids', Unisex)\n\nFormat: single line of comma-separated keywords, most important first.\nDo NOT use sentences or conversational filler.\n\nExample for shoes: sneakers, shoes, white, leather, laces, low-top, Men's\nExample for shirts: t-shirt, crew neck, blue, cotton, striped, Men's\n\nHere is what the user said about the image:\n{{$json.imagePrompt}}",
